U}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Lithuania|Lithuania]]\n|1,062\n|24\n|101\n|<ref>[https://koronastop.lrv.lt/ Svarbiausia informacija apie koronavirus\u0105 (COVID-19)] ''lrv.lt''accessed 14 April 2020</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BIH}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n|1,040\n|39\n|206\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|MKD}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in North Macedonia|North Macedonia]]\n|854\n|38\n|44\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://makfax.com.mk/makedonija/%d0%b2%d0%b8%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%be-%d1%83%d1%88%d1%82%d0%b5-%d1%88%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82-%d0%bb%d0%b8%d1%86%d0%b0-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b7%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b8%d0%b2%d0%bd%d0%b8-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%ba%d0%be%d1%80%d0%be/ |title=\u0423\u0448\u0442\u0435 \u0448\u0435\u0441\u0442 \u043b\u0438\u0446\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0437\u0438\u0442\u0438\u0432\u043d\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441, \u0432\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043d\u043e 18 |date=14 March 2020 |website=Makfax |language=mk |access-date=14 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316040526/https://makfax.com.mk/makedonija/%d0%b2%d0%b8%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%be-%d1%83%d1%88%d1%82%d0%b5-%d1%88%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82-%d0%bb%d0%b8%d1%86%d0%b0-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b7%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b8%d0%b2%d0%bd%d0%b8-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%ba%d0%be%d1%80%d0%be/ |archive-date=16 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|SVK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Slovakia|Slovakia]]\n|769\n|2\n|107\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BUL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bulgaria|Bulgaria]]\n|695\n|35\n|81\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mh.government.bg/bg/informaciya-za-grazhdani/potvrdeni-sluchai-na-koronavirus-na-teritoriyata-na-r-blgariya/ |title=\u041f\u043e\u0442\u0432\u044a\u0440\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0438 \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441 COVID-19 \u0432 \u0411\u044a\u043b\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0438\u044f |date=1 Apr 2020 |website=mh.government.bg |language=Bu